---
title: Pan-Fried Sea Bass in Szechuan-Style Sauce with Crispy Shallot Rice
description: Golden pan-fried sea bass is draped in stir-fried veggies and drizzled with a punchy Szechuan sauce.  Aromatic shallot rice adds another level of complexity and flavour!
